oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Woman near Cumberland river
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Woman, wearing blouse and skirt with dark shoes, standing on gravel road looking out over the Cumberland River (toward the left) near Carthage, Tennessee. Photograph also shows a farm in the background.
